text: Orrmaesia is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Drilliidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Orrmaesia include: * Orrmaesia ancilla (Thiele, 1925) Tucker, J.K. 2004 Catalog of recent and fossil turrids (Mollusca: Gastropoda). Zootaxa 682:1-1295 * Orrmaesia dorsicosta Kilburn, 1988 * Orrmaesia nucella Kilburn, 1988 ;Species brought into synonymy: * Orrmaesia innotabilis W.H. Turton, 1932: synonym of Orrmaesia ancilla (K.H.J. Thiele, 1925) ==References== ==External links== Category:Gastropod genera
